The paper deals with image manipulation and forgery detection, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper specifically focuses on copy-move forgery, which is a type of image manipulation and falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The proposed method involves statistical analysis, which is a common technique used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
